  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of coconut oil in a wok or large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and stir-fry for 1 minute.",
    "Add the mixed vegetables and stir-fry for 2-3 minutes or until they start to soften.",
    "Add the salmon fillets, chili flakes, fish sauce, and sugar free soy sauce. Stir-fry for 2-3 minutes or until the salmon is cooked through.",
    "Add the brown rice to the wok or skillet and stir-fry for 1-2 minutes or until it's lightly toasted.",
    "Transfer the salmon and rice mixture to a serving bowl.",
    "Sprinkle the peanuts and mint leaves on top of the salmon.",
    "Serve with lime wedges on the side.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Garnish with additional mint leaves if desired.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
  ],
